original_script = "IF warmasterState == 0 | GOTO | WAR_0
IF warmasterState == 1 | GOTO | WAR_1

WAR_0
DIALOG | Warmastah | Heya, ape-man. Ye lookin' for gun's, ya? Is good, all good.
DIALOG | Warmastah | They call me Warmastah. Me be the quartermaster and it so happon we gotta loads o gun's tah spare. Ya interested?
QUEST  | warmasterState = 1
GOTO   | SHOPPING_CHOICE

SHOPPING_CHOICE
CHOICE | Check out Warmastah's warez?
REPLY  | CHECK_IT | Yeah, let's see 'em!
REPLY  | CHECK_NO | Nah...

CHECK_IT
IF gunsbag == 20 | GOTO | GUNSBAG_FULL
EVENT | o_wst_warmaster01 | 5
QUEST | shopObject = o_wst_warmaster01 // So I can get local vars
SHOP  | open | War Warez
EVENT |  o_wst_warmaster01 | 6
IF shop == bought_toomuch | DIALOG | P_NAME | I filled up my gun'sbag, I have to stop shopping...

GUNSBAG_FULL
DIALOG | P_NAME | Whoops, my gunsbag is full. Guess I'll shop some other time...

CHECK_NO
EXIT   |

WAR_1
DIALOG | Warmastah | Heya, ape-man. Back for more, ya?
GOTO   | SHOPPING_CHOICE"
